:::'''Sheila:''' Sorry, I have never been in contact with other androids. But I am glad you have put me in the same category with other normal humans.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052206_23-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052206_23-->
::'''Sheila:''' Your words remind me of something. Earlier when I was providing guiding services for the Department of Galactic Geopolitics, everyone spoke to me very politely, and they never avoided me during conversations.
::'''Sheila:''' However, I got the feeling that they did not see me as one of them... and they spoke about a lot of things that I had no knowledge of. All I could do was stand there and pretend I don't exist.
::'''Sheila:''' I wonder what I have to do in order to integrate into their social circle, and be able to join in their conversations.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Teach her to surf the Internet)
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052816-->
::'''Sheila:''' "Net Surfing"? So this is a term on the internet. I thought the internet exists to provide me with upgrades and learning materials. One second, let me check.
::'''Sheila:''' I'd like to learn more about human behavior online. What are people interested in? What do they talk about? I'm so curious about these things...
::'''Sheila:''' So that's how people socialize in a virtual setting? The topics are a bit weird, but they have me intrigued.
::'''Sheila:''' Reviewing curriculum, please do not disturb.
::'''Sheila:''' ...
::'''Sheila:''' I got it! Oh my goodness, my dear (Trailblazer)! I want to rub your face into your skull with flowers!
::'''Sheila:''' AYO {{MC|m=GigaChad|f=GigaChadette}}, have you checked out that trending news everyone in the cosmos has been going on about? Something about rare creature photos and whatnot.
::'''Sheila:''' Yikes, it's a SIN that such an ugly alien creature exists! It's soooo ugly that I had to pop my eyes out and rinse them with holy water!
::'''Sheila:''' Hiya, forget about this. I still have a lot of reports from the Department of Galactic Geopolitics to deal with. Oof.
::'''Sheila:''' Er, something on my face? You got a problem with what I just said? I've got 1300 likes from the virtual community. I'm something of a legend myself! Didn't see that coming, huh?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052206_35-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052206_35-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I get the feeling you've been led astray...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052827-->
::'''Sheila:''' Gosh no. You taught me well! Haha, the Internet is FUN!
::'''Sheila:''' Everyone in the virtual world deserves a podcast. Who needs work when you have homies online? Ah, speaking of work, old Gunn would like to have a chat with you after today's lesson. Don't forget to talk to him when you find time!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
