::'''Sheila:''' Mr. Gunn... Okay, {{MC|m=mister|f=miss}}, please teach me.
::'''Sheila:''' Although I have mastered a lot of advanced knowledge, there is still a big gap between me and ordinary humans. I want to be a real human like everyone else.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052207_10-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052207_10-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Alright. Tell me what your dream is.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052905-->
:::'''Sheila:''' Dream? In the dictionary entry for this word, it is defined as a word that radiates the dazzling light of a star.
:::'''Sheila:''' But my dream is very ordinary, far from being "dazzling." I just want to be a human being who can be accepted by everyone.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What do you want to learn?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052908-->
:::'''Sheila:''' I want to learn... knowledge that will make me more human.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052207_16-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052207_16-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} But you are an android after all...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052910-->
::'''Sheila:''' ...I know, in the physical sense, I can never become a real human.
::'''Sheila:''' But I wanna be accepted and liked. I want to be the kind of person on whom others can place their hopes. I want people to like me.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052207_20-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052207_20-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are their expectations for you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052913-->
:::'''Sheila:''' Yes, I always remember. I am an android, but everyone has always had high expectations for me. I can't disappoint them.
:::'''Sheila:''' I remember that researchers from other departments want me to expand my scope of work to cover their fields, and I also remember how Mr. Gunn wants me to not be led astray. I remember these things...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then what kind of person do you want to become?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052916-->
:::'''Sheila:''' ...If I can... I do not want to let everybody down. I want to make people happy and become part of human society.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052207_26-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052207_26-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Tell her she should be herself.)
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052918-->
::'''Sheila:''' Be myself... How do I do that? "Listen to your heart, follow your dream." This is what some search results suggest. Let me try.
::'''Sheila:''' Reviewing curriculum...
::'''Sheila:''' Learning in progress, please do not disturb.
::'''Sheila:''' ...
::'''Sheila:''' (Trailblazer), thank you for your guidance. I found records of people's private life that they uploaded to the virtual network.
::'''Sheila:''' Despite the little useful information I found, I'm still very intrigued to explore the outside world.
::'''Sheila:''' If I got the chance, I'd go to other planets and use my steps to measure how big those worlds are. I want to feel the sensation of wind and sand brushing past my face.
::'''Sheila:''' As for my life now, I don't see the need to continue living it. It's so boring. I might as well discard it altogether.
::'''Sheila:''' The world outside is so big and I really should go out and have a look. Right, I should starting packing now!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_300052207_37-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_300052207_37-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I get the feeling you've been led astray...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300052928-->
::'''Sheila:''' No, if you didn't give me this opportunity to explore who I really am, I wouldn't realize that freedom is such a precious thing, and I wouldn't have the opportunity to see how big the outside world is.
::'''Sheila:''' Mr. Gunn said that when the lesson is finished, he would like to have a word with you. As for me, I'm going to pack my stuff and get ready to leave...
