:::'''Sheila:''' But I believe the Department of Galactic Geopolitics will certainly try its best to make up for this disaster.
:::'''Sheila:''' If you are not well mentally, I can help you relieve some stress. This is the least I can do for the space station.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
