:::'''Sheila:''' Thought experiments can exercise people's mental capacity and help me understand them. It helps me to get along with the researchers.
:::'''Sheila:''' When the crisis passes, would you like to have a try?
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} About Mr. Gunn...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500010318-->
:::'''Sheila:''' Mr. Gunn is the founder of the Department of Galactic Geopolitics. He is very wise and philosophical.
:::'''Sheila:''' I am sure you will gain a lot of interesting knowledge if you talk to him more.
:::'''Sheila:''' Especially about Fool's Play. I don't think anyone will know more about it than him.
